'''''The Secret of Bastow Manor''''' is a 1983 [[graphic adventure]] game for the [[VIC-20]] and [[Commodore 64]] published by SoftGold in 1983. The Commodore 64 version is formally titled '''''The Secret of Bastow Manor 64'''''.

[[Image:Secret of bastow manor 01.gif|left|thumb|250px|Opening puzzle, entering the manor]]

The graphics use [[PETSCII]] characters<ref>{{cite web|url=http://reset.cbm8bit.com/uploads/files/magazines/57cfedb86749e_Reset08_January2016.pdf|title=Reset No. 8|website=Reset.cbm8bit.com|accessdate=28 December 2018}}</ref> and the game is written in [[BASIC]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://segaretro.org/The_Secret_of_Bastow_Manor|title=The Secret of Bastow Manor|website=Segaretro.org|accessdate=28 December 2018}}</ref>

